Controllexperient

Read and preprocess Control-data

if (!require("pacman")) install.packages("pacman")
library(pacman)
p_load(tidyverse)
p_load(R.utils)
sourceDirectory("./source/")
data<-readControl()  %>% preproControl()

check Accuracy

library(dplyr)
library(sjPlot)
## Warning in checkMatrixPackageVersion(): Package version inconsistency detected.
## TMB was built with Matrix version 1.2.12
## Current Matrix version is 1.2.8
## Please re-install 'TMB' from source or ask CRAN for a binary version of 'TMB' matching CRAN's 'Matrix' package
group_by(data,kategory,session) %>% 
  summarize(mean_corr= mean(corrResp),sd_corr=sd(corrResp),mean_RT=mean(rtResp),sd_RT=sd(rtResp))
p <- ggplot(data=data, 
             aes(x = corrResp, y =rtResp, color= inSet) )+geom_point()
p+facet_grid(kategory  ~  session,margins = T)

fit_corrResp<-lm(corrResp~session*kategory,data = data)
aov(fit_corrResp)
## Call:
##    aov(formula = fit_corrResp)
## 
## Terms:
##                   session  kategory session:kategory Residuals
## Sum of Squares   0.240000  1.973333         1.360000 30.700000
## Deg. of Freedom         4         2                8       135
## 
## Residual standard error: 0.4768725
## Estimated effects may be unbalanced
sjp.lm(fit = fit_corrResp)

fit_corrRespset<-lm(corrResp~inSet*kategory,data = data)
summary(fit_corrRespset)
